<br>
The meeting was cancelled needlesstosay...<br>
<br>
I logged on Malaehi and sat in EC and just stared at the /ooc /shout spam...<br>
<br>
I was a small child when my parents drove through south Memphis, through burning neighborhoods... when Martin Luther King was shot... <br>
<br>
Since then... so many deaths, hijackings, assassinations and disasters, natural and manmade...<br>
<br>
And to think... it isn't over yet.<br>
